1-	LCN: 98963261
 Tawwa, Fadi Ilyas. al-Manakh wa-al-as'ar wa-al-amrad fi 
Bilad al-Sham fi 'ahd al-Mamalik (846-922 H/1250-1516 M) 
/ Fadi Ilyas Tawwa. Bayrut : F.I. Tawwa, 1998. $20.00 
(U.S.). 590 p. : ill., map ; 24 cm. Includes 
bibliographical references (p. 557-569) and indexes. On 
climates; economics, prices and diseases in Sham, 
Mamelukes period, 1250-1516; history. 
 
 
